GL - Class in com.mumfrey.liteloader.gl
Convenience class for working with Mojang's GLStateManager: It would be pretty tolerable to work with GLStateManager as a static import were it not for the fact that you still need to import the GL namespaces themselves from LWJGL in order to get the constants, and also have to deal with the fact that GLStateManager's methods don't have "gl-style" names, making it annoying to work with.
